                        <h3>Fact Checking Thoughts Worksheet</h3>
                        <p>The Fact Checking Thoughts worksheet helps clients to recognise that their thoughts are not
                            necessarily true. It can be difficult to accept the idea that thoughts are not facts at first, especially when we are in
                            the throes of an emotion. However, completing this worksheet will help you come to this
                            realisation.</p>
