                        <div class="category2">
                        <h3>Anxiety Coping</h3>
                        <p>The Coping Skills: Anxiety worksheet describes four strategies for reducing anxiety. Strategies include deep breathing, progressive muscle relaxation, imagery, and challenging irrational thoughts. These coping strategies can help your clients deal with anxiety when it arises, as well as contributing to long-term anxiety relief.</p>
                        <a href="cbt-page2" class="btn btn-general btn-gradient">Get In Touch</a>
                    </div>
                    </div>
                    <img src="cbtmainpageimage/2.jpg"class="img-size2"alt="Ent1">
                   </article>
