                      <div>
                        <div class="category2">
                        <h3>Core Beleif</h3>
                        <p>Use this core beliefs worksheet to help educate clients and get them to think about how their thoughts affect their mood and behavior. This CBT worksheet can also serve as a good take-home reminder after having a discussion about core beliefs.</p>
                        <a href="cbt-page4" class="btn btn-general btn-gradient">Get In Touch</a>
                    </div>
                    </div>
