                        <h3>How to Use the Cross-sectional CBT Model</h3>
                        <p>A cross-sectional formulation takes a ‘snapshot’ of what is going on during a single moment in time. The Exploring Problems Using A Cross-Sectional Model worksheet identifies the key aspects of the cognitive behavioral therapy (CBT) model</p>
                        <a href="cbt-page6" class="btn btn-general btn-gradient">Get In Touch</a>
